2. Now **map** over `chemists`:

```js {1,13}

const listItems = chemists.map(person =>

<li>

<img

src={getImageUrl(person)}

alt={person.name}

/>

<p>

<b>{person.name}:</b>

{' ' + person.profession + ' '}

known for {person.accomplishment}

</p>

</li>

);

```

3. Lastly, **return** the `listItems` from your component:

```js

return <ul>{listItems}</ul>;

```

