### Updating state based on the previous state {/*updating-state-based-on-the-previous-state*/}

Suppose the `age` is `42`. This handler calls `setAge(age + 1)` three times:

```js

function handleClick() {

setAge(age + 1); // setAge(42 + 1)

setAge(age + 1); // setAge(42 + 1)

setAge(age + 1); // setAge(42 + 1)

}

```

